{"type": "article", "id": 3830, "title": "B&O PLAY H2 头戴式耳机", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-24T22:16:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233344eR8b9q5zjmtHSwLn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦视听品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 旗下副线品牌成员 B&amp;O PLAY 日前推出了头戴式耳机系列 H2。这一次品牌邀请了丹麦的设计师 Jakob Wagner 来设计这一系列的新品，设计师希望能够通过耳机的款式展示穿戴者的性格。此外，H2 还内置了麦克风与遥控设备以及一个定制的 40 mm 的 Bang &amp; Olufsen 驱动与低音接口，丰富使用者的听觉体验。不同于 B&amp;O PLAY 的其他耳机，H2 选用的制作材质更加质轻耐久，不会给用户的头部带来压迫感，提供碳素蓝、云朵银以及宝石绿 3 种颜色，定价 199 美元，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00OW2PJP8/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00OW2PJP8&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=tjd14-20&amp;linkId=I2CQDLYK2SRXSK4U\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233341Y28TlsGpUMZr37kz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233342sOnFNVWv7zCqJAej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233342uPIMoaTBckVYlUdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.11875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333430UDpRP1F9Ei3Zvl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233343k2znyKOx8XWG4dt7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233344K7rHpF94eNZ5tWqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}